{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/SteamWhitelist.gif?t=1680646167\" /><br><br><br><i><u>You think you can just escape out of this house? Hahahaha.... NO!</u></i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/Steam.gif?t=1680646167\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>The Story about this game:</u></strong></h2>You are a <strong>detective</strong> who has just <strong>returned</strong> to the house where the <strong>Smith</strong> family lived, because your <strong>grandparents</strong> are <strong>missing</strong> and this was their <strong>last</strong> address and so you decided to <strong>find</strong> them. But what you don't know is that this <strong>decision</strong> is going to be a<strong> horror trip</strong> for you. Because this house is <strong>not empty</strong> and the Smiths <strong>still live</strong> here. By <strong>solving</strong> the <strong>puzzles</strong> and <strong>mysteries</strong> in this horror house you get all the <strong>informations</strong> about the Smith family, what is happening here and about your grandparents. But don\u2019t <strong>lose</strong> yourself along the way and, most <strong>importantly</strong> TRY TO <strong>SURVIVE</strong>! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/SteamScreenshot003.png?t=1680646167\" /><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180630/extras/TestLogo__1_.png?t=1680646167\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>What is this game?</u></strong></h2>Seductive Solitude is a <strong>horror game</strong> that will keep you on the edge of your seat. It's <strong>scary</strong>, but it's also <strong>full</strong> of <strong>suspense and surprises</strong>. You'll <strong>never</strong> know what's going to h